race.comment: WARRIOR PAGE (4) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 4 lengths (23.24) at this track. The form from her last run stacks up well. Has winning claims on her best figures. ONCIDIUM (3) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing seventh (23.56) at this track. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. CHLOE MAY (8) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 400m behind Inflection Point (23.55) in a Grade 6. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. INDI BEAR (1) must be included in calculations.
